ont-size: large;\"><strong>#別再扮受害者，讓外國害怕成為受害者！</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">#816轉美元!</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n#香港人！有禮貌！<br />\n#團結！不分化！不篤灰！不割蓆！<br />\n#Be water！Be Humble！<br />\n#816轉美元!<br />\n#各有各做！齊上齊落！<br />\n#612 721 805 811 812<br />\n#讀稿位係陷阱, 推到唔俾佢哋讀到稿！<br />\n#好重要！唔塞鐵！直入機場！<br />\n#和理非勇武！團結d好無！"},{"pid":"b3a421ee9c5e5aee0f176e3548e8a3ca5ae89fbf","tid":1459294,"uid":84741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:01:07.000Z","msg":"國際投訴之都<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2742ef6036fb60f7f27ff5a4cb6dbb0e3a96583","tid":1459294,"uid":277362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:09:11.000Z","msg":"我想睇子健笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251f5ad35f511116481d3bf0c3097615bef2c9e8","tid":1459294,"uid":90716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:58:46.000Z","msg":"811晚我同家人係康怡食飯，間拉麵店經理九點幾已經收到風要員工走。<br />\n我地食完再係Aeon行左一陣，保安十點三左右同我地講特別事件要提早關 (本身十一點先關)，之後就閂左c岀口付近所有閘，要我地由二樓向康山走。<br />\n十點半左右我地兜翻岀康怡就見到大量狗同速龍跑過。<br />\n大量示威者係太古c岀口同街上跑，如果Aeon無提早關既話，肯定少啲人被拘捕。<br />\n同時我有朋友係太古站內聽到職員同示威者講只有c岀口安全。<br />\n懷疑康怡同地鐵同警察夾埋伏擊示威者，請佢地交代清楚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q2VEw88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq2VEw88.png&h=9b6b4833&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4BQw7Hw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4BQw7Hw.png&h=7ebfa24d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"258552662adc594f72a0971eb6b294014fc7f5a6","tid":1459294,"uid":266755,"lik